<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
    <title>Task Erledigt</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #4CAF50;
            --bg: #f8f9fa;
            --text: #2d3436;
        }
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg);
            color: var(--text);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .card {
            background: white;
            width: 85%;
            max-width: 400px;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            border-radius: 24px;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            text-align: center;
            animation: slideUp 0.5s ease-out;
        }
        .checkmark-circle {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            background: #e8f5e9;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            margin: 0 auto 20px;
            color: var(--primary);
            font-size: 40px;
            animation: scaleIn 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275) 0.2s both;
        }
        h1 { font-size: 24px; margin: 0 0 10px; }
        p { font-size: 16px; color: #636e72; line-height: 1.5; }
        .uid-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #dfe6e9;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-family: monospace;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        @keyframes slideUp {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }
        @keyframes scaleIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.5); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="card">
    <div class="checkmark-circle">âœ“</div>
    <h1>Erledigt!</h1>
    <p>Die Aufgabe wurde erfolgreich als abgeschlossen markiert.</p>
    <div class="uid-badge">ID: {{uid}}</div>
    <div class="uid-badge">Summary: {{summary}}</div>
</div>
</body>
</html>